<p>Wow! Okay, it's good to see this back and in a completely incomprehensible but otherwise legible format! :D</p>
<p>From the log, I get the sense that this was just a complete breakdown in reality. I love lines like &quot;Vernon is getting nosy.&quot; showing up in exploration logs, you had my upvote there. Also &quot;I want to feel his little baby toes.&quot; in <em>any</em> context, geez. Good stuff.</p>

