														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3619266">
									

<p>You flatter me so, I am happy to get such a glowing review of my works~! I didn't feel like I could post it as a mainlist skip and have it get as good of a reception as it has has. However, you can headcanon anything, you can even totally ignore mainlist skips. So I think that this tale can be &quot;canonized&quot; in the same way. And it's not an SCP, it's a URA, or Unregistered Anomaly. It's the designation given to anomalies that are recognized but not placed in the database yet in any way. Basically, this anomaly was being investigated and was in the process of becoming an SCP when this shit went down and it went off the radar.</p>
<p><span style="font-size:25%;">and yes, ophite is one of my fav authors :3</span></p>
<p>EDIT: Though now the General Electric mention has been changed to a <em>different</em> company&#8230;</p>

